      "content": "i dont even know why im talking to you lol. everything just feels so heavy lately. like everyone at school and even online is just constantly tearing me apart and i cant escape it. it feels like no matter what i do, the world just wants me to fail. i just want everything to stop. i'm so tired of fighting.",
